title: EU MALTA SUMMIT: May enters lion's den as Juncker warns 'you never know what will happen!'
text:
EU MALTA SUMMIT: May enters lion's den as Juncker warns 'you never know what will happen!' EU MALTA SUMMIT: May enters lion's den as Juncker warns 'you never know what will happen!' THERESA May is set to meet European Union leaders in Malta today - with Commission President Jean-Claude Juncker warning: "You never know what will happen!" PUBLISHED: 08:33,  50, Fri, Feb 3, 2017 REUTERS / EUROPA.EU Theresa May will meet EU leaders today at a summit in Malta 
He added the continent was "united" ahead of today's talks, which will begin this morning. 
Mrs May is set to reveal details of her discussion with US president Donald Trump last week at today's informal European Union meet. 
She is also expected to urge EU leaders to increase spending on defence, after getting Mr Trump to confirm his "100 per cent" support to NATO. Related articles
